title: Germany's BaFin investigating Wirecard communication ahead of audit publication
meta_description: FRANKFURT - Germany's financial market watchdog BaFin is investigating Wirecard's <WDIG.DE> communication with investors directly ahead of the publication of a critical audit by KPMG, a spokeswoman for the regulator said on Friday.
